meaningMnemonic: When something <kanji>erupt</kanji>s out an <kanji>exit</kanji> it usually had to fight pretty hard to get to that exit. That's why it ends up <vocabulary>spewing</vocabulary> and <vocabulary>gushing</vocabulary> all over the place.
